Superb slideshow wordpress plugin is a strong cross browser fade in slideshow script that incorporates some of your most requested features all rolled into one. Each instance of a fade in slideshow on the page is completely independent of the other, with support for different features selectively enabled for each slide show (This is the updated version of superb slide-show plug-in).
